paintable
=========
Paintable is a jQuery plugin that makes any HTML <canvas> element paintable

Usage
Download and include paintable.js
    <script src="paintable.js"></script>
Call paintable
    $('#canvas').paintable();

Initializing paintable creates a paintable canvas, allowing users to draw on it. You can change tools and colors or do other things by calling methods.

Methods
.paintable('setTool', toolName)

toolName can be "pencil" or "eraser"

.paintable('setColor', color)

.paintable('save')

.paintable('undo')
